        "checksum": "4734feedf8553eb8a571d9cc8215134d0fe04aa55027bb89222612c8dda65692_1_1_1_0_",
        "ggviiph8ERl_text": "<p>Omnis AntiAge Night Cream • 50ml</p>",
        "ggSzrYgvgcA_text": "<p><strong>4.6 Excellent</strong> | 3,439+ reviews</p>",
        "ggVLmbUDTCI_text": "<p>\"I've been using it for 2 weeks,<br>they tell me I look 10 years younger!\"</p>",
        "gg81WwevIKk_childItem_0": "<p>100% Made In Italy</p>",
        "gg81WwevIKk_childItem_1": "<p>Dermatologically Tested</p>",
        "gg81WwevIKk_childItem_2": "<p>For a Healthier and Younger Face</p>",
        "ggbsEHDd1cH_label": "Add to Cart",
        "ggbsEHDd1cH_outOfStockLabel": "Out of stock",
        "ggbsEHDd1cH_unavailableLabel": "Unavailable",
        "ggbsEHDd1cH_variantSelectionRequiredMessage": "Please select a variant to add product to cart",
        "ggjU9YlrJZq_text": "Delivery in 24-48 hours",
        "ggd3njxJyN7_text": "60-day Guarantee",
        "ggCdVdus-lO_text": "<p>If the product doesn't meet your expectations, you have up to 60 days to request a complete refund, without any complications.</p>",
        "ggB9Gp8U8JQ_childItem_0": "<p>Who is it for?</p>",
        "ggB9Gp8U8JQ_childItem_1": "<p>Can it be found in stores/pharmacies?</p>",
        "ggB9Gp8U8JQ_childItem_2": "<p>How long does it last?</p>",
        "ggB9Gp8U8JQ_childItem_3": "<p>How to use it?</p>",
        "ggB9Gp8U8JQ_childItem_4": "<p>How long does it take to see results?</p>",
        "ggB9Gp8U8JQ_childItem_5": "<p>Can you pay on delivery?</p>",
        "ggKZrkCgfQz_text": "<p>The Omnis night face cream is perfect for:</p><ul><li>\n<strong>Men 40+ </strong>who want to reduce wrinkles, dark spots and dry skin</li></ul><p><br>Even though our creams are designed for male skin, they can also be used by <strong>women.</strong></p>",
        "ggLuQ0nuQN8_text": "<p><strong>NO</strong> at the moment<strong> the Omnis cream is only available on our website.</strong></p><p> </p><p>We have chosen to sell only online to <strong>maintain competitive prices</strong> by avoiding intermediaries and <strong>offer</strong> a shopping experience with <strong>personalized advice</strong> for each customer on WhatsApp, which would not be possible in physical stores.</p>",
        "ggR8kqovO2L_text": "<p>Using it every evening, it lasts between 1 and 2 months. You really need very little. 50 ml bottle.</p>",
        "ggFipoBsWwP_text": "<p><strong>In the evening, </strong>after cleaning and drying your face, apply 1-2 doses on the clean face and massage with circular movements until completely absorbed. Bring the excess along the neck.</p>",
        "ggNgskm7d42_text": "<p>Based on the experiences of <strong>multiple customers</strong>, you can already see the first results after the <strong>first days of use</strong>, until you get <strong>completely regenerated skin</strong> after 8 weeks of application.</p>",
        "ggg59nFYXJE_text": "<p>Of course! You will receive your order in 24/48 hours and you can pay in cash on delivery.RetryClaude can make mistakes. Please double-check responses.</p>"
      }
    },
