    "gp_global_section_578689344378766209-9": {
      "type": "gp-global-section-578689344378766209",
      "settings": {
        "section_preload": "false",
        "checksum": "",
        "ggEWS0HyaFY_text": "Dermatologically <span style=\"color:#0156B4;\">Tested in Italy </span>🇮🇹",
        "ggKNKvSk1wm_text": "Dermatologicamente<br><span style=\"color:#0156B4;\">Testato in Italia </span>🇮🇹",
        "gg35OU3qs2i_text": "<p>All Omnis creams are <strong>Made in Italy,</strong> produced by a <strong>laboratory with 70 years of experience.</strong></p><p> </p><p>❌ Non Troverai: siliconi, parabeni, alcool, profumi sintetici. E ovviamente NON testiamo su animali!</p>"
      }
    },
    "gp_global_section_578994961920295705-10": {
      "type": "gp-global-section-578994961920295705",
      "settings": {
        "section_preload": "false",
        "checksum": "",
        "ggCKxnWloLD_text": "Do You Still Have <span style=\"color:#0155B6;\">Any Doubts</span>?",
        "ggQVgYjz4RJ_childItem_0": "<p>Can I use it in SUMMER too since it contains retinol...?</p>",
        "ggQVgYjz4RJ_childItem_1": "<p>Is it available in stores/pharmacies?</p>",
        "ggQVgYjz4RJ_childItem_2": "<p>Is it suitable for sensitive skin?</p>",
        "ggQVgYjz4RJ_childItem_3": "<p>Does it leave a greasy feeling on the skin?</p>",
        "ggQVgYjz4RJ_childItem_4": "<p>How long does it take to see results?</p>",
        "ggQVgYjz4RJ_childItem_5": "<p>How long does it last?</p>",
        "ggQVgYjz4RJ_childItem_6": "<p>How do you use it?</p>",
        "ggQVgYjz4RJ_childItem_7": "<p>What is the complete list of ingredients?</p>",
        "ggQVgYjz4RJ_childItem_8": "<p>Can you pay on delivery?</p>",
        "ggkCktYhb1__text": "<p><strong>Yes, you can use it safely even in summer.</strong><br><br>Omnis contains <strong>Retinyl Palmitate,</strong> a gentle and stable form of vitamin A that does NOT make the skin sensitive to the sun like other more aggressive types of retinol.<br><br>Retinyl Palmitate:</p><ul>\n<li>Does not cause irritation or redness</li>\n<li>Does not increase sensitivity to UV rays</li>\n<li>Can be used all year round without problems<br><br> </li>\n</ul><p><strong>Tip: </strong>As always when exposing your skin to the sun, use SPF 30+ sun protection during the day. This applies to everyone, regardless of the products you use.<br>The Omnis cream is formulated precisely to be used 365 days a year, summer included.</p>",
        "ggvB4QVVEaP_text": "<p><strong>NO</strong> at the moment <strong>Omnis cream is only available on our website .</strong></p><p> </p><p>We've chosen to sell exclusively online to <strong>maintain competitive prices</strong> by avoiding intermediaries and <strong>offering </strong>a shopping experience with personalized recommendations for each customer via WhatsApp, something that wouldn't be possible in physical stores.</p>",
        "ggbUHOmTnxs_text": "<p><strong>No problem!</strong> Our products are suitable for all skin types, even the most sensitive.</p>",
        "ggRc5Y_1poF_text": "<p>Absolutely NO! The consistency is super light, refreshing and with a light touch of lavender</p>",
        "ggCBDbaKf6F_text": "<p>Using it every night, it lasts between 1 and 2 months. A very small amount is all you need. 50 ml bottle.</p>",
        "ggOXNDMBmah_text": "<p><strong>In the evening, </strong>after cleaning and drying your face, apply 1-2 doses on the clean face and massage with circular movements until completely absorbed. Bring the excess along the neck.</p>",
        "ggrsN-dkHKO_text": "<p>The main ingredients are <strong>hyaluronic acid</strong> and <strong>retinol.</strong><br><br>INCI<br><br>Aqua, propylene glycol, glycerin, caprylic/capric triglyceride, hydrogenated ethylhexyl olivate, glyceryl stearate se, aloe barbadensis leaf juice, sodium polyacrylate, phenoxyethanol, hydrogenated olive oil unsaponifiables, tocopherol, tetrasodium glutamate diacetate, urea, trehalose, ethylhexylglycerin, hydrolyzed rice protein, lavandula angustifolia oil, propanediol, sorbitol, linalool, lecithin, olive oil peg-8 esters, helianthus annuus seed oil, tocopheryl acetate, hydroxyethylcellulose, sodium hyaluronate, potassium sorbate, sodium benzoate, xanthan gum, benzyl alcohol, sodium ascorbyl phosphate, limonene, retinyl palmitate, daucus carota sativa root, ascorbic acid, citric acid.</p>"
      }
    },
